name: Tribe Elders - Baba Malik
description:
An awesome and wonderful character.
Hard boned and lovely.
Cheerful and gracious.
A beacon of Hope in any difficult time.
A born leader and fighter.
Yet now he is the one feeling ever so closely tuned to the Earth. 
His skin a canvas depicting the far reaching geography of his heart.
The love for his people keeps the grass growing and helps the leaves fall from the trees.
He is Baba Malik.
King of all natural on earth.
